    <link href="http://muyuu.github.io/WaterDrop/2015/04/02/This-blog-made-Hexo/"/>
    <id>http://muyuu.github.io/WaterDrop/2015/04/02/This-blog-made-Hexo/</id>
    <published>2015-04-01T15:56:30.000Z</published>
    <updated>2015-04-01T16:15:29.000Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>This blog made Hexo that is a static site generator written by Node.js.</p>
<p>I can’t remembered make pages flow. so I write there this post.</p>
<h2 id="need-to-use-Hexo"><a href="#need-to-use-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="need to use Hexo"></a>need to use Hexo</h2><ul>
<li>Node.js</li>
<li>Hexo</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="Install"><a href="#Install" class="headerlink" title="Install"></a>Install</h2><h3 id="Install-Node-js"><a href="#Install-Node-js" class="headerlink" title="Install Node.js"></a>Install Node.js</h3><p>First, install Node.js.</p>
<p>Access the web page and download binary file.</p>
<h3 id="install-Hexo"><a href="#install-Hexo" class="headerlink" title="install Hexo"></a>install Hexo</h3><p>Hexo install is very easy. put the key.</p>
<figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ npm install hexo-cli -g</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>after you can use ‘hexo’ command.</p>
<h2 id="make-new-blog"><a href="#make-new-blog" class="headerlink" title="make new blog"></a>make new blog</h2><p>move directory and hexo command.</p>
<figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> new/blog/parent/dir</div><div class="line">$ hexo init</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>great!</p>
<h2 id="install-npm-packages"><a href="#install-npm-packages" class="headerlink" title="install npm packages"></a>install npm packages</h2><p>move new blog directory. and npm package install</p>
<figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ <span class="built_in">cd</span> blogname</div><div class="line">$ npm install</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="make-new-post"><a href="#make-new-post" class="headerlink" title="make new post"></a>make new post</h2><p>put command</p>
<figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo new <span class="string">'title'</span></div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>has maked source/_posts/title.md.</p>
<p>you write text this file using markdown when finished save file.</p>
<h2 id="check-local-server"><a href="#check-local-server" class="headerlink" title="check local server"></a>check local server</h2><p>start local server.</p>
<figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo server</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>access to <a href="http://0.0.0.0:4000/" target="_blank" rel="external">http://0.0.0.0:4000/</a></p>
<h2 id="generate-static-files"><a href="#generate-static-files" class="headerlink" title="generate static files"></a>generate static files</h2><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo generate</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>if you want deploy when generate files add option ‘–deploy’ or ‘-d’.</p>
<h2 id="deploy"><a href="#deploy" class="headerlink" title="deploy"></a>deploy</h2><figure class="highlight zsh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">$ hexo deploy</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>Notice. before deploy you must be deploy setting at _config.yml file.</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="comment"># Deployment</span></div><div class="line"><span class="comment">## Docs: http://hexo.io/docs/deployment.html</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">deploy:</span></div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  type:</span> git</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  repo:</span> git@github.com:name/repo.git</div><div class="line"><span class="attr">  branch:</span> gh-pages</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="P-S"><a href="#P-S" class="headerlink" title="P.S."></a>P.S.</h2><p>Fight me.</p>
]]></content>
    
